R. Cannings, H.Dwivedi and Z. Lackey. *Haking sur le Web 2.0*
:   Pearson Education France, 2008. ISBN: 978-2-7440-2306-4. Côte BU:
    005.8 CAN. Badly written, translated even worse, and essentially
